'''羅拔圖·馬天尼斯·蒙特柳'''（{{lang-es|'''Roberto Martínez Montoliú'''}}，{{bd|1973年|7月13日|catidx=Martinez, Roberto}}）是一名[[西班牙|西班牙]]前[[職業|職業]][[英式足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[中場|中場]]，退役後擔任現時擔任[[領隊_(足球)|領隊]]，曾先後執教[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|史雲斯]]，[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|韋根]]和[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:埃弗顿; zh-hk:愛華頓;}-]]。现时担任[[比利時國家足球隊|比利时国家足球队]]主教练。

== 生平 ==
=== 球員 ===

==== 早年 ====
馬天尼斯出生於[[西班牙|西班牙]][[加泰罗尼亚|加泰罗尼亚]][[莱里达省|莱里达省]][[巴拉格尔|巴拉格尔]]（Balaguer），在[[皇家薩拉戈薩|薩拉戈薩B隊]]出道，曾於1993年獲提升上一隊出戰[[马德里竞技|马德里竞技]]<small><ref>{{cite web |language=es |url=http://www.heraldo.es/noticias/maestro_ingles.html |title=Maestro de inglés |publisher=heraldo.es |date= |accessdate=2009-12-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140427023305/http://www.heraldo.es/noticias/maestro_ingles.html |archivedate=2014-04-27 }}</ref></small>，於1994/95年球季轉投家鄉球隊[[西丙|西丙]]的[[CF_Balaguer|CF 巴拉格尔]]（CF Balaguer），協助球隊獲得「西班牙協會盃」（Copa Federación de España）亞軍。

==== 韋根 ====
1995年夏季[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|韋根]]的大老闆[[戴夫·韋倫|戴夫·韋倫]]（Dave Whelan）親自從[[西班牙|西班牙]]簽入馬天尼斯及其兩名同伴沙巴（Jesús Seba）及戴亞斯（Isidro Díaz），3人稍後被韋根球迷合稱為「三個朋友」（''The Three Amigos''），於1995/96年球季揭幕日一同首次披甲出戰[[吉林汉姆足球俱乐部|基寧咸]]，馬天尼斯並射入1球，其鬥牛士式慶祝方式令球迷津津樂道。11月11日馬天尼斯與戴亞斯成為首兩位參賽[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]的西班牙球員，馬天尼斯在這場對[[Runcorn_F.C._Halton|倫科恩]]（Runcorn）的-{比}-賽又射入1球，是這項最古老的足球競賽首名西班牙入球者。球季結束馬天尼斯以13球成為球隊首席射手，更入選「[[英格蘭職業足球運動員協會|PFA]][[英格蘭足球聯賽|丙組]][[PFA年度最佳陣容|年度最佳陣容]]」，但球隊在聯賽煞科日主場不敵[[北安普顿足球俱乐部|諾咸頓]]而失去參加附加賽的席位，季後沙巴因不適應[[英國|英國]]的生活而返回[[皇家薩拉戈薩|薩拉戈薩]]。1996/97年球季韋根在聯賽煞科日擊敗[[曼斯菲尔德城足球俱乐部|曼斯菲]]贏得聯賽冠軍及升班[[英格蘭足球聯賽|乙組 〈第三級〉]]，馬天尼斯是陣中主將。戴亞斯於1998年離隊轉投[[罗奇代尔足球俱乐部|罗奇代尔]]，而馬天尼斯繼續效力韋根，更在[[天空電視|天空電視]]兼任西班牙足球評述員，亦時常為球隊擔任大使角色探訪學校。2000/01年球季對[[韦康比流浪者足球俱乐部|韋甘比]]時被罰首面[[紅牌|紅牌]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/1249206.stm |title=Wycombe 1-2 Wigan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2001-03-31 |accessdate=2009-12-07}}</ref></small>，季後附加賽兩回合累計1-2不敵[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]後，遭時任領隊[[斯蒂夫·布鲁斯|布魯士]]放棄，諷刺的是布魯士數日後亦離隊轉投[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宮]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/crystal_palace/1362215.stm |title=Bruce takes up Palace post |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2001-05-31 |accessdate=2009-12-07 |archive-date=2003-01-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030101132622/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/crystal_palace/1362215.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，雖然有韋根球迷呼籲新領隊[[保罗·杰维尔|杰维尔]]重新聘用馬天尼斯，惟最終不了了之。馬天尼斯在韋根效力6季，正選上陣180場，再加上47場後補上陣，合共射入23球。2004年[[BBC|BBC]]足球網站由網民選出馬天尼斯成為韋根歷來的「邪典英雄」（All-time Cult Hero）<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/football_focus/4000175.stm |title=Wigan's cult heroes |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-11-12 |accessdate=2009-12-07}}</ref></small>。

==== 馬瑟韋爾及華素爾 ====
2001年7月3日馬天尼斯以自由身加盟[[蘇超|蘇超]]球會[[马瑟韦尔足球俱乐部|馬瑟韋爾]]，簽約3年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/1421073.stm |title=Martinez joins the Motherwell set |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2001-07-03 |accessdate=2009-12-07}}</ref></small>，2002年4月陷入財困的馬瑟韋爾申請中期債務重組（interim administration）<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/1949818.stm |title=Scottish football's 'biggest crisis' |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-04-25 |accessdate=2009-12-07}}</ref></small>，馬天尼斯成為19名被裁減的球員之一<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/motherwell/1958230.stm |title=Motherwell axe 19 players |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-04-29 |accessdate=2009-12-07 |archive-date=2004-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040617163956/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/m/motherwell/1958230.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，期間只曾8次正選及8次後補上陣。他隨後於8月重返[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]加盟[[沃尔索尔足球俱乐部|華素爾]]，但他卻不能掙到常規正選席位，只獲派1次正選及5次後補上陣，但在這短短數場[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲聯賽]]中，在對[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]時人生第二次領[[紅牌|紅牌]]被驅逐離場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=4873 |title=Walsall 0-2 Reading |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2002-08-31 |accessdate=2009-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071203180801/http://www.soccerbase.com/players_details.sd?playerid=4873 |archive-date=2007-12-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref></small>。

==== 史雲斯 ====
2003年1月馬天尼斯以短期合約形式加盟位列聯賽榜末的[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|史雲斯]]直到球季結束<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/2703119.stm |title=Swans complete Martinez deal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-01-28 |accessdate=2009-12-06}}</ref></small>，2月13日作客[[马科斯菲尔德足球俱乐部|馬爾斯菲]]下半場一記25[[碼|碼]]砲彈式射球為球隊鎖定3-1勝局，自[[节礼日|节礼日]]後首次脫離榜尾席位<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/2716169.stm |title=Macclesfield 1-3 Swansea |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-02-13 |accessdate=2009-12-07}}</ref></small>，3月22日作客[[京达米士特足球俱乐部|京达米士特]]，馬天尼斯再發長砲，對方門將未能接牢來球，被[[蘭尼·約翰羅斯|蘭尼·約翰羅斯]]（Lenny Johnrose）門前「執死雞」扳平1-1，在主隊再度領先後，馬天尼斯憑22碼外[[自由球|自由球]]「彎」入扳平2-2，為球隊取得寶貴1分<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/2852837.stm |title=Kidderminster 2-2 Swansea |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-03-22 |accessdate=2009-12-07}}</ref></small>，球隊在聯賽煞科日4-2擊敗[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|侯城]]成功護級保持[[英格蘭足球聯賽|聯賽]]資格<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/2976539.stm |title=Swansea 4-2 Hull |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-05-03 |accessdate=2009-12-07 |archive-date=2017-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170801084400/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_3/2976539.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2003年6月馬天尼斯獲得這支[[威爾斯|威爾斯]]球隊一紙兩年長約<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/2986042.stm |title=Martinez chooses Swansea |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-06-23 |accessdate=2009-12-07}}</ref></small>。2003/04年球季初馬天尼斯觸傷[[膝蓋|膝蓋]][[韌帶|韌帶]]缺陣6星期<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/3156419.stm |title=Oxford Utd 3-0 Swansea |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-08-25 |accessdate=2009-12-07}}</ref></small>。他其後在[[積遜·史密夫|積遜·史密夫]]（Jason Smith）退役後獲委任為[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]，在史勿夫受傷期間，馬天尼斯已代行隊長職務<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/3225171.stm |title=Martinez takes Swans helm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-10-29 |accessdate=2009-12-07}}</ref></small>，但史雲斯的隊長臂章像被詛咒，多名隊長先後傷出<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/3196551.stm |title=Nugent ends captaincy jinx |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-08-31 |accessdate=2009-12-07}}</ref></small>，在他傷愈僅上陣3場後，於操練時觸傷同一個膝蓋再缺陣4星期<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/3227871.stm |title=Martinez blow for Swans |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-10-30 |accessdate=2009-12-07}}</ref></small>，尚幸暫時無須動[[手術|手術]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/3310109.stm |title=Martinez boost for Swans |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2003-12-12 |accessdate=2009-12-07}}</ref></small>。新領隊[[肯尼·杰基特|杰基特]]上任後仍然由馬天尼斯擔任隊長<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/3874645.stm |title=Martinez suits Jackett |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-07-07 |accessdate=2009-12-07}}</ref></small>，而球隊於2004/05年球季遷移到新建的[[自由球場|自由-{}-球場]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/3919299.stm |title=Jackett lauds new stadium |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-07-23 |accessdate=2009-12-07}}</ref></small>。季初馬天尼斯一度被領隊棄用<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/3554426.stm |title=Swansea reassure Martinez |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-08-11 |accessdate=2009-12-07}}</ref></small>，但他誓言重奪席位<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/3574690.stm |title=Martinez fights for future |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-08-17 |accessdate=2009-12-07}}</ref></small>，最終以隊長身份帶領球隊升班[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]，並在[[FAW超級盃|FAW超級盃]]（FAW Premier Cup）決賽2-1擊敗[[雷克斯汉姆足球俱乐部|域斯咸]]中成為最佳球員<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_of_wales/4538679.stm |title=Triumphant exit delights Jackett |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-05-11 |accessdate=2009-12-06}}</ref></small>。2006年5月約滿被球隊棄用<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/5029242.stm |title=Swansea release skipper Martinez |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-05-30 |accessdate=2009-12-08}}</ref></small>。

==== 車士打城 ====
馬天尼斯以自由身加盟[[英乙|英乙]]球會[[切斯特城足球俱乐部|車士打城]]，簽約兩年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/chester/5227006.stm |title=Chester snap up ex-Swan Martinez |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-07-29 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>，8月5日聯賽揭幕戰主場2-0擊敗[[艾宁顿斯坦利足球俱乐部|阿克寧頓]]首度為球隊上陣；8月26日作客[[托奎联足球俱乐部|托基聯]]，於完場前射入扳平2-2<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/5266084.stm |title=Torquay 2-2 Chester |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-08-26 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>；9月30日主場對[[布里斯托流浪足球俱乐部|布里斯托流浪]]馬天尼斯再取得入球，為車士打城鎖定2-0勝局<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/5373630.stm |title=Chester 2-0 Bristol Rovers |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-09-30 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>。10月28日作客0-1負於[[巴尼特足球俱乐部|班列特]]，馬天尼斯於完場前5分鐘被球證出示第二面[[黃牌|黃牌]]後驅逐離場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/6072602.stm |title=Barnet 1-0 Chester |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-10-28 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>，賽後車士打城更被[[英格蘭足球總會|英格蘭足球總會]]指控球員行為不檢<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/chester/6121378.stm |title=Chester City are handed FA charge |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-11-06 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>，判罰1,000[[英鎊|英鎊]]及作出警告<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/chester/6291619.stm |title=Chester handed £1,000 fine by FA |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-01-23 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>。12月9日主場4-1大勝[[林肯城足球俱乐部|林肯城]]，馬天尼斯先拔頭籌取得本季第3個入球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/6201654.stm |title=Chester 4-1 Lincoln |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-12-09 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>。直到2007年2月15日[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|史雲斯]]領隊[[肯尼·杰基特|杰基特]]與球隊解約，馬天尼斯被視為可能接班人選之一<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/6364593.stm |title=Swansea part company with Jackett |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-02-15 |accessdate=2009-12-09 |archive-date=2007-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070225180611/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/6364593.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，2月21日主場1-0擊敗[[貝里足球俱樂部|貝利]]成為他的球員生涯告別戰<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/6371181.stm |title=Chester 1-0 Bury |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-02-21 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>，2月24日他重返史雲斯出任領隊<small><ref name="Swansea boss">{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/6389531.stm |title=Martinez appointed Swansea boss |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-02-24 |accessdate=2009-12-09 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305002141/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/6389531.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

=== 領隊 ===
==== 史雲斯 ====
雖然有超過50人應徵[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|史雲斯]]領隊之職，其中不乏有名氣及經驗的人選，經面試後，史雲斯仍然鍾情其前隊長馬天尼斯這名年僅33歲的新丁，由於他仍然有約在身，史雲斯需要向[[切斯特城足球俱乐部|車士打]]作出賠償，馬天尼斯動筆簽約兩年，由於已過了轉會窗時限，本季是車士打正選主力兼[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]的馬天尼斯不可落場擔任球員，只可專心領隊職務<small><ref name="Swansea boss"/></small>。2007年2月24日作客0-1負於[[约维尔足球俱乐部|伊奧維]]，馬天尼斯只作壁上觀<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6371153.stm |title=Yeovil 1-0 Swansea |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-02-24 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>，雖然球隊與附加賽席位有5分距離，馬天尼斯仍希望帶領球隊爭取升班<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/6393363.stm |title=Martinez sure of Swansea success |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-02-25 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>。2月27日馬天尼斯正式執教的首場-{比}-賽作客對[[罗瑟勒姆足球俱乐部|洛達咸]]，驚濤駭浪下以2-1險勝而回<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6392421.stm |title=Rotherham 1-2 Swansea |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-02-27 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>。3月16日主場2-0擊敗[[切斯特菲尔德足球俱乐部|車士打菲特]]後史雲斯重返附加賽區域<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/6461905.stm |title=Martinez salutes play-off 'boost' |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-03-17 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>。聯賽煞科日主場面對全力爭取自動升級席位的[[黑池足球會|黑池]]，需要淨勝4球才可參加附加賽的史雲斯以3-6落敗，這是馬天尼斯執教12場以來的第二場敗仗，而史雲斯亦緣盡附加賽<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6603011.stm |title=Swansea 3-6 Blackpool |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-05-05 |accessdate=2009-12-09 |archive-date=2009-01-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090104032617/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/6603011.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

季後馬天尼斯隨即展開重建球隊陣容工作<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/6630665.stm |title=Martinez plans early rebuilding |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-05-06 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>，首先從[[蘇格蘭足球甲級聯賽|蘇甲]][[圣庄士东足球俱乐部|聖莊士東]]以象徵費用簽入[[贾森·斯科特兰|史葛蘭特]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/6674397.stm |title=Swans sign Scotland from Saints |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-05-25 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>，繼而簽入兩名[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]球員[[杜魯斯·德·弗里斯|德·弗里斯]]及[[Ferry_Bodde|菲里·伯德]]（Ferry Bodde）、兩名[[西班牙|西班牙]]球員[[安赫尔·兰格尔|兰格尔]]及[[Guillem_Bauza|居莱姆·鲍萨]]（Guillem Bauza）、[[Matthew_Collins|马特蒂·科林斯]]（Matthew Collins）、[[Darrly_Duffy|达瑞尔·杜菲]]（Darrly Duffy）及從[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]借用[[保羅·安德森_(足球運動員)|安德森]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/6899840.stm |title=Swans progress pleases Martinez |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-07-15 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>，但球隊亦失去效力四年來每季射入超過20球的[[Lee_Trundle|李·特伦德勒]]（Lee Trundle）<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/6906383.stm |title=Trundle seals £1m Bristol C move |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-08-01 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>，9月初再從[[阿拉维斯竞技|艾拉維斯]]免費簽入[[Andrea_Orlandi|安得雷·奥兰迪]]（Andrea Orlandi）<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/6973591.stm |title=Swansea sign Feeney and Orlandi |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-09-01 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>。

[[2007年至2008年英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|2007/08年球季]]史雲斯表現慢熱，開季頭8場僅取得3勝2和3負位列聯賽榜第10位，但踏入10月後，球隊4戰4勝，於月中4-1擊敗[[伯恩茅斯足球俱乐部|般尼茅夫]]後進佔榜首位置<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7044613.stm |title=Martinez not getting carried away |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-10-15 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>，馬天尼斯更獲選「[[英甲|英甲]]10月份最佳領隊」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7071207.stm |title=Martinez scoops monthly accolade |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-11-01 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>。11月5日[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|韋根]]辭退[[基斯·赫澄斯|基斯·赫澄斯]]（Chris Hutchings）後有傳聞馬天尼斯是接任人選<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7079558.stm |title=Martinez linked with Wigan post |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-11-05 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>。在主場大部分時間僅10人應戰3-2擊敗勁敵[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]後，史雲斯在榜首以5分領先次席[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|諾定咸森林]]踏入新年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7164873.stm |title=Martinez proud of his super Swans |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-12-30 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>，馬天尼斯再獲選為「[[英甲|英甲]]12月份最佳領隊」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7169810.stm |title=Martinez handed managerial award |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-03 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>。新球季引入多達11員新面孔，為陣中各球員帶來良性競爭<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7205646.stm |title=Swansea boss hails squad rivalry |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-24 |accessdate=2009-12-10}}</ref></small>，馬天尼斯的改革漸見成果，2008年1月25日作客4-0大勝前列份子[[唐卡斯特流浪足球俱乐部|唐卡士打]]後，領先優勢更增加到11分<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7210732.stm |title=Swans ready to push on - Martinez |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-26 |accessdate=2009-12-10}}</ref></small>，1月29日作客0-0賽和次席的[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|諾定咸森林]]仍然以10分帶出，更保持12場不敗戰績<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7217190.stm |title=Robinson confident of promotion |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-30 |accessdate=2009-12-10}}</ref></small>，馬天尼斯蟬聯「[[英甲|英甲]]1月份最佳領隊」，首度全季執教即3次獲選「每月最佳領隊」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7219771.stm |title=Martinez scoops monthly accolade |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-31 |accessdate=2009-12-10}}</ref></small>。2月22日主場1-0擊敗[[卢顿足球俱乐部|盧頓]]是馬天尼斯任教一週年的最佳禮物，球隊帶先14分及保持14場不敗，是英甲入球最多及失球次少的球隊，在他首年任內史雲斯56戰取得35勝12和僅9負的驕人成績<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7257571.stm |title=Martinez magic motivates Swans |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-02-22 |accessdate=2009-12-10}}</ref></small>。4月12日作客2-1擊敗[[吉林汉姆足球俱乐部|基寧咸]]後確保升班資格，是史雲斯24年來首次重返次級聯賽<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_of_wales/7344663.stm |title=The Swans are going up! |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-04-12 |accessdate=2009-12-10}}</ref></small>。4月17日雖然主1-2負於護級份子[[约维尔足球俱乐部|伊奧維]]，由於次席的[[卡莱尔联足球俱乐部|卡素爾]]同日亦負於[[绍森德足球俱乐部|修安聯]]，史雲斯提早兩輪贏得[[英甲|英甲]]聯賽冠軍<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/7344100.stm |title=Swansea champions despite defeat |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-04-19 |accessdate=2009-12-10}}</ref></small>。4月23日馬天尼斯續簽一份沒有透露年期的長約<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7352739.stm |title=Martinez agrees 'improved' deal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-04-23 |accessdate=2009-12-10}}</ref></small>。球季煞科日作客1-0擊敗[[布莱顿足球俱乐部|白禮頓]]後，史雲斯取得歷來最多的92分，賽後高舉聯賽冠軍獎盃的馬天尼斯形容這是一個「奇妙」的球季<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7382455.stm |title=Martinez hails 'fantastic' Swan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-05-03 |accessdate=2009-12-10}}</ref></small>。5月13日獲[[英格蘭足球聯賽領隊協會|英格蘭足球聯賽領隊協會]]選為「英甲年度最佳領隊」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7397679.stm |title=Martinez crowned manager of year |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-05-13 |accessdate=2009-12-10}}</ref></small>。

季後馬天尼斯再從[[西班牙|西班牙]]引入[[佐迪·高美斯|高美斯]]及[[Gorka_Pintado|哥卡·平塔多]]（Gorka Pintado）<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7436259.stm |title=Spanish duo complete Liberty move |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-06-06 |accessdate=2009-12-10}}</ref></small>，及以破球會轉會費紀錄的40萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]將上季借用的[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾斯國腳]][[艾殊利·威廉斯|威廉斯]]收歸旗下<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7398940.stm |title=Swans complete Williams signing |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-05-22 |accessdate=2009-12-10 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003030330/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7398940.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，而提出轉會要求的菲里·伯德亦被球隊挽留<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/7431111.stm |title=Bodde hands in transfer request |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-06-02 |accessdate=2009-12-10}}</ref></small>。

==== 韋根 ====


==== 愛華頓 ====
2013年6月5日獲[[英超|英超]]球會[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]聘任接替[[大衛·莫耶斯|莫耶斯]]擔教，簽約四年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22750453 |title=Roberto Martinez: Everton appoint former Wigan manager |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2013-06-05 |accessdate=2013-06-05 |archive-date=2013-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131026163223/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/22750453 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。<br />

2013/14赛季，埃弗顿开局不利，前三轮全部打平，马丁内斯随后在转会窗口关闭前从切尔西租借[[羅美路·盧卡古|盧卡古]]，从曼城租借[[加雷斯·巴里|巴里]]，球队在第四轮主场1-0力克切尔西后获得了三连胜，在第七轮做客1-3输给曼城后，埃弗顿迎来了十轮不败（6胜4平），直到节礼日主场0-1输给桑德兰，进入2014年，埃弗顿在自3月1日开始豪取联赛七连胜，一度掌握着争四的主动权，但在最后五轮联赛中仅获得2胜3负无缘欧冠资格，即便如此，埃弗顿本赛季仍以21胜9平8负积72分的成绩刷新了球队在英超的最高积分记录，并顺利拿到欧战资格。

2014/15赛季和2015/16赛季，埃弗顿在投入众多的情况下，连续两个赛季排名英超第11名，马丁内斯在2016年5月12日被埃弗顿解雇<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.evertonfc.com/news/2016/05/12/club-statement |title=Club Statement |publisher=''Everton FC'' |date=2016-05-12 |accessdate=2016-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160814082329/http://www.evertonfc.com/news/2016/05/12/club-statement |archive-date=2016-08-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

==== 比利时 ====
2016年8月4日，比利时足协任命罗伯托·马丁内斯为比利时国家队新一任主教练。在[[2018年世界盃|2018年世界盃]]，马丁内斯所帶領的比利時國家隊，一洗過去在國際大賽中不團結的陋習，取得世界盃季軍<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/matches/match/300331536/#match-summary |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2018-07-14 |archive-date=2018-12-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181224181957/https://www.fifa.com/worldcup/matches/match/300331536/#match-summary |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 私人生活 ==
2009年6月26日馬天尼斯與其[[蘇格蘭人|蘇格蘭]]女友貝芙·湯臣（Beth Thompson）在[[斯旺西|斯旺西]]的「聖約瑟教堂」（St Joseph's Cathedral）結婚，兩人於2001年在[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]相識，當時馬天尼斯正效力[[马瑟韦尔足球俱乐部|馬瑟韋爾]]。馬天尼斯情迷「[[Nocilla|西德白朱古力醬]]」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/6951597.stm |title=Grilling the chief Swan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-08-17 |accessdate=2009-12-09}}</ref></small>。

